name: Unityprojects-samples
tagline: Sample code from various games I've developed in Unity (C#)
body:
### Welcome to my GitHub project page.
This page hosts some sample code, and a screenshot from a 2D shoot 'em up game I developed with the Unity engine during my free time (as well as to learn C# in a more engaging and rewarding way).  

The files you will find here are just a few scripts from the game that showcase some of my C# skills. 

### Authors and Contributors
Brian Hornak  

University of Maryland Class of 2019  

Electrical Engineering
